News.Title: Advance Agrolife Q3FY26 Results Published
News.Summary: Advance Agrolife Limited published its unaudited standalone financial results for the quarter and nine months ended December 31, 2025, in compliance with SEBI regulations.

News.Title: Advance Agrolife Board Meet on Feb 7 for Q3 Results
News.Summary: Advance Agrolife Limited has scheduled its board meeting for February 07, 2025, to consider and approve unaudited financial results for Q3FY26 and nine months ended December 31, 2025.

News.Title: Advance Agrolife Reports Q2 FY2026 Financial Results with Revenue of ₹226.29 Million
News.Summary: Advance Agrolife Limited announced unaudited financial results for the quarter and half-year ended September 30, 2025, showing revenue from operations of ₹226.29 million for the quarter. The agrochemicals company's board approved the results on November 14, 2025, with earnings per share of ₹1.99 for the quarter.
